FBIS3-917 "drafr051_d_94007" FBIS-AFR-94-051 Document Type:Daily Report 12 Mar 1994 SOUTHERN AFRICA Malawi Electoral Commission Extends Voter Registration EA1203204294 Blantyre Malawi Broadcasting Corporation Network in English 1800 GMT 12 Mar 94 EA1203204294 Blantyre Malawi Broadcasting Corporation Network Language: English Article Type:BFN [Excerpt] The Electoral Commission has announced the extension of the voter registration period from today to 26 March. Making the announcement today in Blantyre, a spokesman for the commission said it was clear that extra time was needed to give voters a chance to register. The spokesman called on all Malawians who will be 18 or more on the ballot day to register their names before the close of the registration on the 26th of this month. [passage omitted]
